Oriental style outdoor awp map. The restaurant and the bank were on kandahar pictures i found online.

ItÂ´s not a small map i`d say. (64 Spawnpoints)
All the custom stuff is compiled into the bsp file and is everything you need to play , unless you run it on your server , then you should put the res file in your maps folder aswell.

I want to thank Steve .:O:. and Karatebug ;) for their submissions too.

Installation :
- put the "awp_kandahar.bsp" file to your ...\Steam\SteamApps\username\counter-strike source\cstrike\Maps
- GL&HF
